                            <comment id="15555822" author="githubbot" created="Fri, 7 Oct 2016 18:14:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;GitHub user mxm opened a pull request:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/2610&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/flink/pull/2610&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-4777&quot; title=&quot;ContinuousFileMonitoringFunction may throw IOException when files are moved&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;FLINK-4777&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;FLINK-4777&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; catch IOException in ContinuousFileMonitoringFunction&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;    FileSystem.listStatus(path) may throw an IOException when it lists files&lt;br/&gt;
    and then retrieves their file status. This is quite common, e.g. editors&lt;br/&gt;
